        {
            "title": "內地1月70大中城市樓價按年跌3.1%　創7個月最大跌幅",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國家統計局公布內地1月70個大中城市新建商品住宅銷售價格，外電據此測算，期內價格指數按年跌3.1%，跌幅比去年12月擴大0.4個百分點，創7個月以來最大跌幅；按月跌幅維持0.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Shutterstock圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230901_FI_China-Property_source_web_-shutterstock_1200.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Shutterstock圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230901_FI_China-Property_source_web_-shutterstock_1200.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Shutterstock圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">統計局表示，上月各線城市商品住宅銷售價格按月降幅總體收窄、按年下降。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上月一線城市新樓樓價按年跌幅擴大0.4個百分點至2.1%，其中，上海升4.2%，北京、廣州及深圳則跌2.4%至5.3%；二、三線城市新樓樓價跌幅亦有所擴大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">按月比較，一線城市新樓樓價跌0.3%，跌幅與上月相同。上海持平，其餘跌0.3%至0.6%；二、三線城市則分別跌0.3%和0.4%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">京滬廣深二手樓價按年和按月都跌，按年跌幅介乎6.5%至8.7%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659786-%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b01%e6%9c%8870%e5%a4%a7%e4%b8%ad%e5%9f%8e%e5%b8%82%e6%a8%93%e5%83%b9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e8%b7%8c3-1%e3%80%80%e5%89%b57%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%80%e5%a4%a7%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230724_FI_source_licensed_China-Property_shutterstock-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-13 10:42:20",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行開展1450億元人民幣逆回購操作　連續5日淨投放",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行公開市場開展1450億元人民幣7日期逆回購操作，利率維持於1.4厘。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">對沖到期量後，單日淨投放1135億元，連續5日淨投放。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">因應春節假期調休上班安排，本周公開市場統計時段直至明日為止。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659709-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e9%96%8b%e5%b1%951450%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e6%b0%91%e5%b9%a3%e9%80%86%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc%e6%93%8d%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%80%e9%80%a3%e7%ba%8c5%e6%97%a5%e6%b7%a8%e6%8a%95%e6%94%be-2",
