            "title": "港股低開392點   重磅股俱跌  海致科技飆逾2倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股恒生指數低開392點或1.45%，報26640點 ; 恒生科技指數跌85點或1.59%，報5323點 ; 恒生國企指數跌112點或1.23%，報9062點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">大市成交46.33億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"海致科技招股書封底\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/02706-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"海致科技招股書封底\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/02/02706-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">海致科技招股書封底</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">海致科技(02706)首掛，較招股價高204.14%，報82.3元，成交居第三位; 沃爾核材(09981)較招股價升0.05%，報20.1元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)跌1.87%，報525.5元，成交居首 ; 阿里巴巴(09988)跌2.9%，報154元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">友邦(01299)跌2.15%，報82元，成交居第二位 ; 港交所(00388)跌2.61%，報403.2元 ; 滙控(00005)跌2.8%，報135.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金(02899)跌3.47%，報43.46元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">永利澳門(01128)跌0.98%，報6.05元。上季經整EBITDAR按年7.45%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15659637-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b392%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e8%82%a1%e4%bf%b1%e8%b7%8c-%e6%b5%b7%e8%87%b4%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be2%e5%80%8d",
